Pure racing! 😍

What a day in Riga, @KristofferssonJohan takes his first win since Spain 2020! 🏆

Catch up on all the weekend action, head over to Red Bull TV for the replays! 📺

#RedBull #RedBullMotorsports #WorldRX #RigaRX
